6 An Act relating to the Oklahoma Veterans Commission;
authorizing the establishment of the State of
7 Oklahoma Veterans Foundation; stating purpose of
Foundation; allowing Foundation to receive
8 contributions; directing incorporation of Foundation;
providing authority for designation of initial
9 membership and election of the board of directors;
prohibiting certain board members from voting on
10 certain matters; prohibiting certain preferential
consideration; requiring financial records to be
11 available for audit; providing certain exceptions;
